      <title>推动“共同繁荣”的中国基金薪酬上限为415,000美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/china-funds-weigh-415-000-pay-cap-in-common-prosperity-drive</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，几家中国共同基金经理提议将员工工资上限限制在 300 万元人民币（41.5 万美元）左右，以响应习近平主席“共同富裕”的倡议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-12/china-funds-weigh-415-000-pay-cap-in-common-prosperity-drive</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 11:09:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
